{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>当你站在一个迷宫里的时候，往往会被错综复杂的道路弄得失去方向感，如果你能得到迷宫地图，事情就会变得非常简单。<p><p>假设你已经得到了一个n*m的迷宫的图纸，请你找出从起点到出口的最短路。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"走出迷宫 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出从起点到出口最少需要走的步数。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行是两个整数n和m(1≤n,m≤100)，表示迷宫的行数和列数。<p><p>接下来n行，每行一个长为m的字符串，表示整个迷宫的布局。字符‘.’表示空地，‘#’表示墙，‘S’表示起点,‘T’表示出口。<p>","examples":"<input>3 3\nS#T\n.#.\n...\n\n</input><output>6\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1254","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}